207
00:18:04,575 --> 00:18:06,276
Doraemon!

208
00:18:07,116 --> 00:18:08,985
Instan Wardrobe Cam!

209
00:18:09,609 --> 00:18:12,079
Draw an outfit.

210
00:18:13,046 --> 00:18:14,414
