262
00:21:59,505 --> 00:22:04,310
No, Noby. Wait!

263
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:08,932
Boy, it's heavy.

264
00:22:12,788 --> 00:22:14,490
Stop!

265
00:22:14,584 --> 00:22:16,953
